<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2012/06/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>fantomas-tool</id>
    <version>4.7.9</version>
    <authors>Florian Verdonck, Jindřich Ivánek</authors>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <license type="expression">Apache-2.0</license>
    <licenseUrl>https://licenses.nuget.org/Apache-2.0</licenseUrl>
    <icon>fantomas_logo.png</icon>
    <readme>README.md</readme>
    <description>This library aims at formatting F# source files based on a given configuration.
Fantomas will ensure correct indentation and consistent spacing between elements in the source files.
Some common use cases include:
(1) Reformatting a code base to conform a universal page width
(2) Converting legacy code from verbose syntax to light syntax
(3) Formatting auto-generated F# signatures.</description>
    <releaseNotes>### Changed
* Add `fable_modules` to the directories which are always excluded. [Fable 3.4](https://github.com/fable-compiler/Fable/releases/tag/3.4.0)

### Fixed
* Let binding after match lambda is moved outside of nested module. [#2214](https://github.com/fsprojects/fantomas/issues/2214)</releaseNotes>
